                    </ul>
                    <p class="feedback-text inline-block" data-bind="text: comfortFeedback"></p>
                </li>

                <li class="list-item">
                    <p class="item-title">Maintenance cost</p>
                    <p class="item-subtitle">Are regular replacement parts reasonably priced? How much does it cost to fix a broken part?</p>

                    <ul class="answer-list item-rating-list" data-list-type="">
                        <li data-value="1" data-bind="click: setMaintenanceCost">Unreasonably High</li>
                        <li data-value="2" data-bind="click: setMaintenanceCost">Very High</li>
                        <li data-value="3" data-bind="click: setMaintenanceCost">High</li>
                        <li data-value="4" data-bind="click: setMaintenanceCost">Reasonable</li>
                        <li data-value="5" data-bind="click: setMaintenanceCost">Well priced</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="clear"></div>
                </li>

                <li class="list-item">
                    <p class="item-title">Value for Money</p>
                    <p class="item-subtitle">How satisfied are you with your motorcycle? Did you get a bike worth your money?</p>

                    <ul class="answer-list item-rating-list" data-list-type="">
                        <li data-value="1" data-bind="click: setValueForMoney">Not at all</li>
                        <li data-value="2" data-bind="click: setValueForMoney">Nah! I am not</li>
                        <li data-value="3" data-bind="click: setValueForMoney">Umm.. Okay</li>
                        <li data-value="4" data-bind="click: setValueForMoney">Satisfied</li>
                        <li data-value="5" data-bind="click: setValueForMoney">Feels great!</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="clear"></div>
                </li>

                <li class="list-item">
                    <p class="item-title">Extra Features</p>
                    <p class="item-subtitle">How often do you use the extra features on your bike? Rate basis the usage of these features.</p>

                    <ul class="item-rating-list inline-block" data-list-type="extraFeatures" data-bind="css: extraFeaturesCount() > 0 ? 'opacity-active' : ''">
                        <li class="bwmsprite" data-bind="click: setRating, attr: {'data-count': 1}, css: extraFeaturesCount() > 0 ? 'star-one' : 'star-zero'"></li>
                        <li class="bwmsprite" data-bind="click: setRating, attr: {'data-count': 2}, css: extraFeaturesCount() > 1 ? 'star-one' : 'star-zero'"></li>
